msgstr "ᱟᱹᱭᱟᱹᱛ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱱᱤᱛᱚᱜ ᱞᱟᱭᱥᱮᱱᱥ ᱫᱚ CC BY 2.0 FR ᱦᱩᱭᱩᱜ ᱞᱟᱹᱠᱛᱤᱭᱟ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L37
msgid "You must be the original creator of the sentence."
msgstr "ᱟᱢ ᱫᱚ ᱟᱹᱭᱟᱹᱛ ᱨᱮᱱ ᱟᱥᱚᱞ ᱥᱤᱨᱡᱚᱱ ᱦᱩᱭᱩᱜ ᱞᱟᱹᱠᱛᱤᱭᱟᱢᱟ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L38
