msgstr "ᱟᱹᱭᱟᱹᱛ ᱫᱚ ᱟᱥᱚᱞ ᱦᱩᱭᱩᱜ ᱞᱟᱹᱠᱛᱤᱭᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱛᱚᱨᱡᱚ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱵᱟᱝ ᱚᱰᱚᱠᱚᱜᱼᱟ ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L53
msgid ""
"Press the following button to start or restart an analysis of which of your "
"sentences can be switched to CC0."
msgstr "ᱟᱢᱟᱜ ᱚᱠᱟ ᱟᱹᱭᱟᱹᱛ ᱠᱚ ᱥᱤᱥᱤ᱐ ᱨᱮ ᱵᱚᱫᱚᱞ ᱫᱟᱲᱮᱭᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱵᱤᱥᱲᱤ ᱮᱦᱚᱵ ᱥᱮ ᱫᱚᱦᱲᱟ ᱪᱟᱹᱞᱩ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱞᱟᱛᱟᱨ ᱨᱮ ᱮᱢ ᱟᱠᱟᱱ ᱵᱩᱛᱟᱢ ᱞᱤᱱ ᱢᱮ ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L55
msgid "Start analysis"
msgstr "ᱵᱤᱥᱲᱤ ᱮᱦᱚᱵ ᱢᱮ"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L62
msgid "Switch license"
msgstr "ᱞᱟᱭᱥᱮᱱᱥ ᱵᱚᱫᱚᱞ ᱢᱮ"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L64
msgid ""
"Press the following button to initiate the license switch of the above-"
"listed sentences."
msgstr "ᱪᱮᱛᱟᱱ ᱨᱮ ᱥᱩᱪᱤ ᱟᱠᱟᱱ ᱟᱹᱭᱟᱹᱛ ᱠᱚ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱞᱟᱭᱥᱮᱱᱥ ᱥᱣᱤᱪ ᱮᱦᱚᱵ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱞᱟᱛᱟᱨ ᱨᱮ ᱮᱢ ᱟᱠᱟᱱ ᱵᱩᱛᱟᱢ ᱞᱤᱱ ᱢᱮ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L68
msgid ""
"Be careful, this operation can not be undone. Switching from CC BY to CC0 is"
" possible, but not the opposite."
msgstr "ᱥᱚᱱᱛᱚᱨᱚᱜ ᱢᱮ, ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱚᱯᱟᱨᱮᱥᱚᱱ ᱫᱚ ᱵᱟᱝ ᱦᱩᱭ ᱫᱟᱲᱮᱭᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱾ CC BY ᱠᱷᱚᱱ CC0 ᱨᱮ ᱵᱚᱫᱚᱞ ᱫᱚ ᱥᱚᱢᱵᱷᱚᱵᱚᱱᱟ, ᱢᱮᱱᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱩᱞᱴᱟᱹ ᱫᱚ ᱵᱟᱝ ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Licensing/switch_my_sentences.ctp#L72
msgid "Switch license to CC0 1.0"
msgstr "ᱞᱟᱭᱥᱮᱱᱥ ᱵᱚᱫᱚᱞ ᱢᱮ ᱥᱤᱥᱤ᱐ ᱑.᱐ ᱨᱮ"

