#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/donate.ctp#L34
msgid "Any question?"
msgstr "ᱡᱟᱦᱟᱱ ᱠᱩᱠᱞᱤ?"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/donate.ctp#L38
msgid ""
"If you have any question regarding donations or if you would like to donate "
"in any other way than the ones mentioned here, you may contact either <a "
"href=\"{trangEmail}\">Trang</a> or the entire <a "
"href=\"{teamEmail}\">team</a>."
msgstr "ᱡᱩᱫᱤ ᱟᱢ ᱴᱷᱮᱱ ᱫᱟᱱ ᱵᱟᱵᱚᱛ ᱡᱟᱦᱟᱱ ᱠᱩᱠᱞᱤ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱟᱨ ᱡᱩᱫᱤ ᱟᱢ ᱱᱚᱸᱰᱮ ᱞᱟᱹᱭ ᱟᱠᱟᱱ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱮᱴᱟᱜ ᱞᱮᱠᱟ ᱫᱟᱱ ᱮᱢ ᱥᱟᱱᱟᱭᱮᱫ ᱢᱮᱭᱟ, ᱟᱢ ᱫᱚ <a href=\"{trangEmail}\">ᱴᱨᱟᱝ</a> ᱟᱨ ᱵᱟᱝ ᱜᱚᱴᱟ <a href=\"{teamEmail}\">ᱴᱤᱢ</a> ᱥᱟᱶ ᱡᱚᱯᱚᱲᱟᱣ ᱫᱟᱲᱮᱭᱟᱜᱼᱟᱢ᱾"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/donate.ctp#L52
msgid "All donations"
msgstr "ᱥᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱫᱟᱱ"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/donate.ctp#L61
msgid "How to donate"
msgstr "ᱪᱮᱫ ᱞᱮᱠᱟ ᱫᱟᱱ ᱦᱩᱭᱩᱜᱼᱟ"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/donate.ctp#L62
msgid "You have two possible ways to make a donation:"
msgstr "ᱟᱢ ᱴᱷᱮᱱ ᱫᱟᱱ ᱮᱢ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱵᱟᱨ ᱥᱚᱢᱵᱷᱚᱵᱚᱱ ᱰᱟᱦᱟᱨ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ:"

#: github.com/Tatoeba/tatoeba2/tree/dev/src/Template/Pages/donate.ctp#L67
msgid ""
"<b>IBAN transfer.</b> This is probably the cheapest way to donate. Tatoeba's"
" bank is based in France, so if you are from an EU country, it is likely "
"that the transfer will be free of charge."
msgstr "&lt;b&gt;IBAN ᱩᱪᱟᱹᱲ᱾&lt;/b&gt; ᱫᱟᱱ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱜᱮ ᱥᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱥᱟᱥᱛᱟ ᱰᱟᱦᱟᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ᱾ ᱛᱟᱴᱚᱭᱵᱟ ᱟᱜ ᱵᱮᱝᱠ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱷᱨᱟᱱᱥ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ, ᱚᱱᱟᱛᱮ ᱡᱩᱫᱤ ᱟᱢ ᱤᱭᱩ ᱫᱤᱥᱚᱢ ᱨᱮᱱ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱢ, ᱮᱱᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱩᱪᱟᱹᱲ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱷᱨᱤ ᱜᱮ ᱦᱩᱭᱩᱜᱼᱟ᱾"

